snippet.title: Slime Rancher PC Game Review - Most Addictive Game of 2017
snippet.description:
Join the Sonny Jim Army on Discord: https://discord.gg/w2JhHv6
Support me on Patreon: http://tinyurl.com/zd48qvf
Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ggdograa
Join the Gggmanlives Steam Group: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/gggmanlives
Reddit Fanpage: http://www.reddit.com/r/Gggmanlives/

Slime Rancher is the tale of Beatrix LeBeau, a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the ‘Far, Far Range’ where she tries her hand at making a living wrangling slimes.
